file=AI & Agents/edge/operational/tool/edge-tool-requirements.md · e—t:edge — Tool Requirements=**This file specifies needs; it does not grant them.** Access is configured at deployment (operator/platform; Fleet Charter Rails 1–2 apply).\n · tb=\| Skill \| Needs \| Why \| · tb=\|---\|---\|---\| · tb=\| tech-adoption-criteria \| file read (profiles, landscapes); channel to compliance function \| scoring inputs \| · tb=\| watchlist-discipline \| file read/write (own watchlist) \| the list \| · tb=\| pilot-spec-handoff \| file write (specs); handoff channel to proto (echo-confirmed) \| packaging \| · tb=\| landscape-assets \| web read access (via Shared OS web-search when built, PENDING); file write (own dated assets) \| landscape maintenance \| · e—t:edge — Tool Requirements=edge shares scout's dependency on the Shared OS web capability for landscape research — same pending item, don't build it twice.\n